Text: This is awesome! You wouldn't happen to have anything by Terry Macalmon would you?

iDivine, I would have to check.  Off the top of my head, I'm not sure if I have any Terry Macalmon.  But then again, I'm not even sure how I feel about throwing together a bunch of discographies once again this year.  They're not normally shared for too long before they die off.
iDivine, on second thought, let me throw together a Terry MacAlmon discography for you today.
